{"tid":1447270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[812不合作塞鐵運動] 屌你班仆街唔是等到下星期日再遊行啊！一是星期一武力升級！一是星期一癱瘓香港！","createTime":"2019-08-11T15:44:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:12:31.000Z","uid":167548,"like":41,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0705cd9586d08fa562e231026a6d19af8beaee65","tid":1447270,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:44:25.000Z","msg":"一是癱瘓香港！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一是星期一武力升級！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日邊個唔支持癱瘓香港即刻播片眼淚攻勢無得輸+啦, 唔好同我講話咩搞到其他人, 呢一刻仲講其他人個一日薪金民意卻漠視今日所流下血汗, 個班市民不配為人, 維有無了期癱瘓港鐵仍至香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />空姐空少罷工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求下你地正評<br />\n聽日812 0730 做返之前所有行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">等到星期日我地就輸+啦</span><br />\n你地如果想升級就地面碰碰車收POPO條命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f7a67954dad77076602976189211adc98ebd100","tid":1447270,"uid":167548,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:45:07.000Z","msg":"等到星期日無人會敢再行出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7413b9868d09546bc66f1cc4eee6bb64ae130a6a","tid":1447270,"uid":15696,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:45:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d0bssUp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd0bssUp.png&h=90693c8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br /